        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Why hast thou forgotten me? - See the notes at Psalm 22:1. He had seemed to forget and forsake him, for He did not come to interpose and save him. This is a part of the prayer which he says Psalm 42:8 that he would use.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Why hast thou forgotten me? - See the notes at ",
            "children": []
          },
