      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Why go I mourning? - On the meaning of the word used here - קדר  qodēr - see Psalm 35:14, note; Psalm 38:6, note. The idea is that of being bowed down, made sad, deeply afflicted, as one forsaken.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Why go I mourning? - On the meaning of the word used here - קדר  qodēr - see ",
            "children": []
