      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Why hast thou forgotten me?",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (see the comment on Psalm 13:1). God does not forget even when he most seems to forget (comp. ",
