        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "because of  the oppression of the enemy?",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Why am. I allowed to remain so long an exile, sorrowing and oppressed (comp. ",
